rComments: He is very genorous and respectible professor.

Prof Avendaño is my favourite professor I've had so far at UofT. He explains concepts so well and is always available for extra help if needed. The KSR field trip was so fun because of his enthusiasm and willingness to go above and beyond to help students understand. THANK YOU

Professor Avendano is a wonderful proff who is always happy to help students outside of class. Tests are very fair and should be pretty straight forward as long as you studied for them. There are several textbooks but they are optional and are not tested. Our class also went on field trips, which were nice breaks from just academics!

Prof. Avendano is one of my fav profs in UofT! He is super nice and ALWAYS passionate and energetic regarding the course content. I really enjoy the field trip that we had and I just feel I can really connect to the profs and share our thoughts! Exam is not very hard as long as you are familiar with all the slides.
